      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI directly linked to the clinical decision question (worst-case hemolysis identification).",
      "rationale": "Normalized Index of Hemolysis (NIH) and scalar stress exposure time (SET) are direct hemolysis surrogates used in regulatory submissions. QoI relevance confirmed by clinical collaborators."
